            <title>[FLINK-3760] Fix StateDescriptor.readObject </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-3760</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The readObject method of StateDescriptor uses uses &lt;tt&gt;ObjectInputStream.read()&lt;/tt&gt;. For very large serialized default values this will not necessarily read all data in one go. We need a loop that reads it in several steps.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
